description: Enterprise techniques used by WINERACK, ATT&CK software S0219 v1.0
name: WINERACK (S0219)

techniques.comment: WINERACK can create a reverse shell that utilizes statically-linked Wine cmd.exe code to emulate Windows command prompt commands.
WINERACK can enumerate files and directories.
WINERACK can gather information about the host.
WINERACK can gather information on the victim username.
